name: GrowthOpportunityAreas
description: In addition to Priority Development Areas (PDAs), many jurisdictions nominated Growth Opportunity Areas (GOAs) at the beginning of the Sustainable Communities Strategy process. GOAs have not yet been adopted by the local City Council or Board of Supervisors; most are recommended to be submitted through the PDA application process.
